---
title: Quick Creamy Chorizo Farfalle with Cherry Tomatoes & Parmesan
description: Golden 'bow ties' of farfalle combine with cherry tomatoes, cream and smokey chorizo to create an elegant meal fit for only the
best. Add a sharp Parmesan garnish for dimension and dinner is complete.
